The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, camping, rock-climbing, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, mystery, scientific, sports
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, analyst, architect, firefighter
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, snowboarding, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, roller, trike
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the firefighter##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the librarian##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the analyst##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the fan of folk##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the librarian is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the fan of pop is the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the fan of indie is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the architect##1
12. the fan of indie is between the person driving the roller and the fan of house##2
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the firefighter##1
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |       4       |
